  "strategy": [
    "Prioritize forward movement when clear.",
    "Use commit states to enforce full turns or rotations until path is clear.",
    "After obstacle detection, require recovery before resuming forward movement.",
    "Allow only one primary controllable action per state (except obs_front for escape).",
    "Prevent oscillation by not offering both turn directions in any state.",
